name: America from its Hills to its Mountains
description: This image, "America from its Hills to its Mountains" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The concept behind this image was to reflect the diverse landforms in America (USA) from its hills, plains, and mountains. The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in the process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewers.
